jjil.algorithm
Class ErrorCodes

java.lang.Object
  jjil.algorithm.ErrorCodes

public class ErrorCodes
extends java.lang.Object

Provides a list of error codes for use in creating Error objects.

J2ME's version of Java unfortunately doesn't support enums. So we simulate them using an old programming trick...
